/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <code><strong>Node.textContent</strong></code> Eigenschaft repräsentiert den Text-Inhalt einer Node und&nbsp;ihrer untergeordneten Elemente.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>text</em> = element.textContent;\nelement.textContent = \"Dies ist ein Beispiel-Text\";\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>textContent</code> gibt&nbsp;<code>null</code>&nbsp;zurück, wenn das Element ein&nbsp;D<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document\" title=\"DOM/Document\">ocument</a>, ein&nbsp;Dokumenten-Typ&nbsp;oder eine&nbsp;Notation ist. Um den gesamten Text und die CDATA Daten für das gesamte Dokument zu bekommen, kann man&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/document/documentElement\" title=\"DOM/document.documentElement\">document.documentElement</a>.textContent</code> benutzen.</li>\n <li>Handelt es sich bei der Node um eine CDATA Sektion, einen Kommentar, eine Prozess-Anweisun oder eine Text-Node, dann gibt&nbsp;<code>textContent</code>&nbsp;den Text in dieser Node zurück (den&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\" title=\"DOM/Node/NodeValue/Node.nodeValue\">nodeValue</a>).</li>\n <li>Für andere Node-Typen gibt <code>textContent</code> die aneinander gehängten&nbsp;<code>textContent</code>&nbsp;Attribute aller Kind-Nodes zurück, aber ohne Kommentare und Prozess-Anweisungen. Dies ist ein leerer String, wenn die Node keine Kinder&nbsp;hat.</li>\n <li>Wenn man diese Eigenschaft setzt, werden alle Kinder der Node ersetzt und mit einer einzelnen Text-Node ersetzt, die den neuen Wert beinhaltet.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"unterschiede_zu_innertext","title":"Unterschiede zu <code>innerText</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Internet Explorer hat&nbsp;<code>element.innerText</code> eingeführt.&nbsp;Die Absicht ist ähnlich, weist aber die folgenden Unterschiede auf:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Während <code>textContent</code>&nbsp;den Inhalt aller Element, inklusive <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Elementen, liefert, macht die&nbsp;IE-spezifische Eigenschaft&nbsp;<code>innerText</code> dies nicht.</li>\n <li><code>innerText</code>&nbsp;kennt den Stil und gibt keinen Text versteckter Elemente zurück, was <code>textContent</code> hingegen tut.</li>\n <li>Da <code>innerText</code>&nbsp;den CSS-Stil kennt, verursacht es einen&nbsp;Reflow, während&nbsp;<code>textContent</code> dies nicht tut.</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Unterschiede zu innerText"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"unterschiede_zu_innerhtml","title":"Unterschiede zu&nbsp;<code>innerHTML</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>innerHTML</code>&nbsp;gibt, wie der Name schon sagt, das HTML&nbsp;zurück. Sehr häufig wird dies benutzt, um den Text aus einem Element abzurufen oder ihn zu ändern. Stattdessen sollte lieber&nbsp;<code>textContent</code> verwendet werden. Da der Text nicht als HTML geparst wird, ist es sehr wahrscheinlich, dass die Performance besser ist.&nbsp;Weiterhin umgeht man so auch einen möglichen XSS-Angriffspunkt.</p>","titleAsText":"Unterschiede zu innerHTML"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Nehmen wir das folgende HTML Fragment:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//   &lt;div id=\"divA\"&gt;Hier ist &lt;span&gt;etwas&lt;/span&gt; Text&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Abrufen des Text-Inhalts:</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"divA\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// |text| wird auf \"Hier ist etwas Text\" gesetzt</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Setzen des Text-Inhalts:</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"divA\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hier ist auch Text\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Das HTML von divA sieht nun so aus:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//   &lt;div id=\"divA\"&gt;Hier ist auch Text&lt;/div&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.Node.textContent","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2004/REC-DOM-Level-3-Core-20040407/core.html#Node3-textContent\" rel=\" noopener\">textContent</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"notes"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"example"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"specification"}],"summary":"Die Node.textContent Eigenschaft repräsentiert den Text-Inhalt einer Node und ihrer untergeordneten Elemente.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.textContent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.textContent","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Node.textContent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/textcontent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/textcontent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent","title":"Node.textContent"}],"pageTitle":"Node.textContent - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}